Dialogue: 5,0:00:01.30,0:00:03.20,Default,N,0,0,10,,{\i1}Older brother Mutta is plagued by bad luck.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:03.20,0:00:07.30,Default,N,0,0,10,,{\i1}Born under a lucky star, younger brother Hibito becomes the first Japanese moonwalker.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:07.30,0:00:13.13,Default,N,0,0,10,,{\i1}Older brother Mutta continues his long quest to the moon, having finally been selected as a backup member.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:13.13,0:00:16.32,Default,N,0,0,10,,{\i1}A lunar accident has left Hibito struggling on the sidelines, suffering from a panic disorder.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:16.32,0:00:20.48,Default,N,0,0,10,,{\i1}But he's able to pass a test to return to active duty.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:20.48,0:00:23.31,Default,N,0,0,10,,{\i1}However, NASA decides that Hibito,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:23.31,0:00:26.29,Default,N,0,0,10,,{\i1}having succumbed to panic disorder, cannot be assigned to a mission,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:26.29,0:00:28.51,Default,N,0,0,10,,{\i1}and Hibito disappears.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:30.00,0:00:30.00,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.55,0:00:47.06,OP,,0,0,0,,I can't get lost in what I'm doing, nothing works out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.06,0:00:49.60,OP,,0,0,0,,I don't want these endlessly dull days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.60,0:00:51.85,OP,,0,0,0,,I hope I can move on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.85,0:00:53.52,OP,,0,0,0,,before the call of freedom drags me away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.52,0:00:55.69,OP,,0,0,0,,What's your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:57.48,OP,,0,0,0,,I just want some real courage
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:01:00.36,OP,,0,0,0,,We all stare doubt in the face, every one of us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.36,0:01:04.28,OP,,0,0,0,,Isn't the unpredictability of life the fun of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.28,0:01:08.04,OP,,0,0,0,,Devote your life to that dream you can't express
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:11.91,OP,,0,0,0,,Let's go, advance against the wind, our road is long
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.91,0:01:15.92,OP,,0,0,0,,Embrace the pain of it too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:19.88,OP,,0,0,0,,Take a big breath now, and yell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.88,0:01:27.76,OP,,0,0,0,,Big Bang! Chase it without fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.76,0:01:37.48,OP,,0,0,0,,I want to dream so badly it amazes me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:46.95,OP,,0,0,0,,There's cowardice in the way of your true wish
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.95,0:01:53.00,OP,,0,0,0,,Rip that hot veil aside
Dialogue: 5,0:02:00.01,0:02:00.01,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.55,0:02:06.48,title,EpTitle,0,0,0,,{\fad(528,685)\fax-0.15\bord0\blur0.5\c&HEFEAED&\4c&H000000&\pos(946,8)}#98 The Ultimate Astronaut
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:06.48,title,EpTitle,0,0,0,,{\fad(528,685)\fax-0.15\1a&HFF&\blur1.5\bord1\3c&H1C2E3A&\pos(946,8)}#98 The Ultimate Astronaut
Dialogue: 5,0:02:05.26,0:02:07.25,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I'm gonna hit the jackpot this time...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:07.25,0:02:12.57,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Because everyone said that store sold to lots and lots of winning people!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:13.17,0:02:16.30,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Furukawa, from the laundry place, won 500,000 yen.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:16.30,0:02:21.82,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,And Shimada, from the Buddhist place, bought five tickets, and won 300,000 yen.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:21.82,0:02:24.18,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I can feel it coming, dear...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:24.18,0:02:25.96,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Billions, billions, billions!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:25.96,0:02:26.87,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,What will we do?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:26.87,0:02:28.84,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Lots and lots?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:28.84,0:02:31.25,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Two winners count as "lots and lots"?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:31.25,0:02:34.18,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Two is a lot!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:34.18,0:02:35.71,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Lots and lots.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.54,0:02:37.63,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Hey, Mom!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:38.05,0:02:41.14,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Hibito's missing again, and it's dark outside.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:41.56,0:02:42.71,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,What? Again?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:42.71,0:02:44.64,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,He wanders off lots and lots.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:44.64,0:02:49.16,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,L-Lots and lots? He's only done it twice!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:49.16,0:02:51.44,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,How can you guys be so relaxed?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.44,0:02:54.33,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Two is a lot.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:54.33,0:02:55.90,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Lots and lots.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:56.42,0:02:58.45,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I'll go out and look for him.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.53,0:03:05.58,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,It's freezing...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:06.12,0:03:09.29,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Man... Where did Hibito go?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.99,0:03:14.49,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do you have to run off without saying anything?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:16.40,0:03:18.26,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,Mr. Mutta.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.97,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,Are you listening, Mr. Mutta?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:22.39,0:03:25.44,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. Sorry, I'm listening.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:25.44,0:03:28.68,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,It appears that you don't understand who this meeting is for.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:31.92,0:03:35.86,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,During the last simulation, communication was a jumbled mess.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:36.14,0:03:40.03,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,You omitted information you should have transmitted to me,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:40.03,0:03:44.99,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,and you also lose points for interrupting me while I was talking.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:45.64,0:03:46.49,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:46.83,0:03:52.25,Default,Larry,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's funny because Vince is usually the one who's constantly interrupting people.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:54.58,0:03:57.34,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,We must be in sync at all times.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:57.92,0:04:03.68,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,If there is any miscommunication, we will be unable to follow the procedure manual.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:04.14,0:04:06.88,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,Next time, try to concentrate harder.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.88,0:04:09.64,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,A moment's lapse can lead to a mission failure,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:10.58,0:04:13.90,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,or even cause an accident.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:14.98,0:04:15.69,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:19.55,0:04:21.32,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}I screwed up...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:22.38,0:04:24.77,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the first day, I did fine...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:25.52,0:04:29.43,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I've been having trouble staying focused.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:29.43,0:04:36.03,Default,A,0,0,0,,Did you tell Hibito that he can't go to space anymore, Butler?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.03,0:04:39.71,Default,But,0,0,0,,No, I wasn't that blunt about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.28,0:04:42.59,Default,But,0,0,0,,But that's probably how Hibito interpreted what I said.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.55,0:04:47.51,Default,B,0,0,0,,He hasn't shown up since last Friday.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:02.82,0:05:04.37,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:04.37,0:05:06.28,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hibito's ignoring me?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:06.98,0:05:09.31,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}He could at least send a reply.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:20.70,0:05:23.87,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been six days since Hibito vanished.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:27.22,0:05:28.59,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've asked the neighbors,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.60,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}his NASA friends,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.22,0:05:34.35,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom and Dad...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.20,0:05:39.24,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}But no one knows where Hibito is.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:51.08,0:05:52.45,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I'm home...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.97,0:06:01.59,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Hey, Mu.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.98,0:06:03.09,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Let's go to bed.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:04.08,0:06:05.84,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Is that all you have to say?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:09.56,0:06:11.30,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:11.62,0:06:15.10,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,I went to the park to take pictures of Virgo.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:16.68,0:06:20.19,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,But all I got was a bunch of dark pictures.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.19,0:06:20.94,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Wanna see?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:21.50,0:06:23.89,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Man...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.94,0:06:29.45,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,If you wander off again, I'm not gonna look for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:29.45,0:06:33.47,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'll let you know next time.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:33.47,0:06:35.83,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Or I'll leave a note.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:37.40,0:06:41.95,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,"Hey, hey! I'm in the park right now, Mu!"
Dialogue: 5,0:06:42.61,0:06:45.10,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,That's the message I sent you with telepathy.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:45.10,0:06:46.34,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,You didn't hear it?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.34,0:06:48.09,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,How could I hear that, fool?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:48.38,0:06:51.72,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Okay, then do you know what I'm thinking now?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:52.40,0:06:54.63,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,I'll send it over!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:56.95,0:06:59.13,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}How would I know, stupid?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.00,0:07:08.19,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,You want me to teach you how to take pictures of Virgo with a camera.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:09.29,0:07:11.30,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Wow, you're right!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:11.30,0:07:12.62,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,That was amazing, Mu!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:13.01,0:07:15.20,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Just so you know, it isn't possible with that camera.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.58,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,So telepathy works!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:17.94,0:07:19.69,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,I guess I'm just as amazing.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:21.00,0:07:24.17,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Then from now on, I'll use telepathy.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:01.10,0:08:03.14,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Is he not coming back?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:03.87,0:08:05.88,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I guess that's fine with me.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:07.32,0:08:10.39,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Since I'll have this huge house all to myself.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:11.55,0:08:13.48,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,And I can drink all the beer.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.64,0:08:26.19,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,And I can sing all I want!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:26.79,0:08:29.53,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,And I can watch whatever I want on TV!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:30.77,0:08:32.48,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:32.48,0:08:35.90,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,There isn't any particular reason for this, but help yourself.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:35.90,0:08:37.07,Default,Ozzy,0,0,0,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:37.74,0:08:41.49,Default,Ozzy,0,0,0,,This isn't necessary, Mutta.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.39,0:08:44.22,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Thanks Ozzy, Ova.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:44.22,0:08:45.21,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.21,0:08:46.82,Default,Ozzy,0,0,0,,Yep, sure thing.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:47.96,0:08:49.39,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Good night!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:49.39,0:08:50.96,Default,Ova,0,0,0,,Good night, Mutta.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.05,Default,Ozzy,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:55.41,0:08:59.45,Default,Ova,0,0,0,,Looks like Hibito still isn't back.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:59.45,0:09:00.77,Default,Ozzy,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:04.43,0:09:07.95,Default,Ozzy,0,0,0,,I didn't expect Hibito to go missing.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:12.98,0:09:15.86,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomorrow, we're looking at sunshine in Texas.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:15.86,0:09:19.49,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\i1}With some clouds rolling in, and a chance of rain.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:19.49,0:09:26.25,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if you keep a smile on your face, rain can't force the sunshine away.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:26.62,0:09:32.25,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}And if you start crying, you'll be raining on any sunny day.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:30.66,0:09:32.25,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I don't recognize this number.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.41,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:37.41,0:09:39.35,Default,But,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, Mr. Mutta.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:39.66,0:09:42.31,Default,But,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's me... Butler.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:43.64,0:09:45.60,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,B-Butler?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:47.54,0:09:52.19,Default,But,0,0,0,,I've been getting concerned because it's been a few days since Hibito came in.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:52.50,0:09:55.84,Default,But,0,0,0,,I could have called him directly,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.84,0:09:58.76,Default,But,0,0,0,,but I thought he might not want to talk to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.92,0:10:03.24,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:04.18,0:10:06.66,Default,But,0,0,0,,Then he didn't tell you anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:10.55,0:10:14.34,Default,But,0,0,0,,Medically, Nanba Hibito is fit.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:14.94,0:10:18.19,Default,But,0,0,0,,He meets all the requirements for an astronaut.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:18.19,0:10:18.97,Default,But,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:21.22,0:10:26.31,Default,But,0,0,0,,NASA has concluded that sending him back to the moon on a mission
Dialogue: 5,0:10:26.61,0:10:29.39,Default,But,0,0,0,,{\i1}isn't worth the risk.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:42.97,0:10:48.79,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did you run off without saying anything to me?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.87,0:10:52.24,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}And you didn't leave a note like you promised.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:55.21,0:10:56.46,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where are you?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:03.32,0:11:05.78,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Say something, Hibito.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:06.98,0:11:09.21,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I thought you could use telepathy.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:10.93,0:11:14.01,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I can't hear a thing!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:19.20,0:11:19.20,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:21.54,0:11:23.20,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:23.20,0:11:27.29,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Didn't Hibito pass the test to return to duty?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:30.68,0:11:32.88,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,He completed the test without an attack.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:32.88,0:11:37.05,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Doesn't that mean he passed?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:43.39,0:11:47.72,Default,But,0,0,0,,During the test, there was a point when Hibito's heartbeat jumped.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.54,0:11:54.06,Default,But,0,0,0,,Of course, this happens to all astronauts...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:55.14,0:11:59.61,Default,But,0,0,0,,But a few of the examiners considered this the sign of a panic attack.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:02.39,0:12:05.93,Default,But,0,0,0,,One of them is the program manager.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:06.83,0:12:12.50,Default,But,0,0,0,,I'm sure you can see that, without his approval, Hibito can't be assigned to a mission.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:14.08,0:12:17.46,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Is the program manager that Gates person?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:18.36,0:12:21.84,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,So if I talk to him and convince him to change his mind...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:23.74,0:12:27.93,Default,But,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, you don't want to do that, Mr. Mutta.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:30.62,0:12:35.62,Default,But,0,0,0,,There's a petition requesting Hibito's reinstatement.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:35.62,0:12:38.48,Default,But,0,0,0,,Four veteran astronauts signed it,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:39.24,0:12:42.65,Default,But,0,0,0,,knowing that they would be subjecting themselves to scrutiny.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.09,0:12:47.23,Default,But,0,0,0,,Damian, Freddy, Eddie Jay, and Azuma.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:49.54,0:12:50.82,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Azuma...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:51.53,0:12:56.14,Default,But,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that still wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:56.14,0:12:58.00,Default,But,0,0,0,,{\i1}You should keep your mouth shut.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:58.80,0:13:03.52,Default,But,0,0,0,,{\i1}One wrong move, and you could lose your chance to go to the moon.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:08.80,0:13:10.31,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Butler...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.17,0:13:14.31,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Does NASA truly believe...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:15.48,0:13:17.94,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,that Hibito is...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:33.62,0:13:35.83,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,The weather's too nice.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:38.86,0:13:40.94,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I came too early...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:49.50,0:13:50.63,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.33,0:13:55.39,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Hibito, don't tell me you lost your cell phone.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:09.03,0:14:10.53,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Hibito...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:11.10,0:14:15.66,Default,Mu,0,0,20,,{\i1}I don't even know if you're still alive.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:15.66,0:14:18.03,Default,Mu,0,0,20,,{\i1}Give me some kind of reply.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:19.39,0:14:22.63,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you don't want to bother, an "A" will work.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:26.30,0:14:30.08,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}Even Mom and Dad are beginning to worry.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:30.08,0:14:33.08,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}If you don't message us, they'll ask the police to start searching for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:34.52,0:14:37.87,Default,Mu,0,0,5,,{\i1}Tell me if you're alive or dead."
Dialogue: 5,0:14:40.76,0:14:46.20,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I even added a light joke that Hibito won't be able to ignore.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.82,0:14:48.10,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Send.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:00.56,0:15:03.59,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,{\i1}CAPCOM, this is landing module Altair.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:04.06,0:15:08.24,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have 233,351 kilograms of fuel remaining.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:08.24,0:15:10.92,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,{\i1}This should be sufficient.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:12.19,0:15:13.30,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Let me confirm.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:13.62,0:15:16.13,Default,A,0,0,0,,Fuel consumption is within expected levels.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.13,0:15:17.18,Default,A,0,0,0,,The mission is a go.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:18.12,0:15:19.78,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Fuel consumption is within expected levels.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:19.78,0:15:21.02,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,You're doing well.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:22.40,0:15:23.31,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger that.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.96,0:15:26.86,Default,A,0,0,0,,I need to run to the restroom.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.07,Default,Dami,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:30.20,0:15:31.82,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Thanks, Damian.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:33.24,0:15:36.54,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I heard you signed a petition requesting that Hibito be reinstated.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:37.71,0:15:39.08,Default,Dami,0,0,0,,I only did what was right.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:40.02,0:15:43.25,Default,Dami,0,0,0,,After a near fatal mistake, I've received the chance to return to the moon.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:44.50,0:15:49.72,Default,Dami,0,0,0,,It makes no sense that Hibito wouldn't be allowed to return, after saving me.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:54.47,0:15:55.54,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:56.36,0:15:59.02,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}This makes no sense at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:00.32,0:16:05.04,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't they understand how hard he worked to get here?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:16.44,0:16:20.34,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do they not have any respect for my brother?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:21.59,0:16:23.42,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,{\i1}CAPCOM, this is Altair.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:23.88,0:16:26.38,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Er, yes! This is Houston.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.38,0:16:29.54,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,Confirm that all thruster nozzles are operational.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:29.54,0:16:30.51,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,Thruster...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:29.54,0:16:32.34,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Er, yes! This is Houston!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:32.34,0:16:35.39,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crap, I interrupted him again.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:35.39,0:16:40.24,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it okay to leave the thruster angle and output on setting A?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:40.24,0:16:41.23,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Let me confirm.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.96,0:16:42.87,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:42.87,0:16:46.31,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right, the flight director isn't currently here.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:47.79,0:16:49.39,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.75,0:16:53.46,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is setting A standard procedure?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:53.46,0:16:54.89,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:54.89,0:16:57.07,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Yes, it should be fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:57.07,0:16:58.58,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Use setting A.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:59.95,0:17:01.41,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger that.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:01.41,0:17:03.79,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,{\i1}We will now commence landing sequence.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:03.79,0:17:05.84,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,{\i1}Current altitude is 2,300 meters.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:10.46,0:17:12.33,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,A warning has sounded.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:12.33,0:17:13.84,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,Please confirm.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:14.12,0:17:17.01,Default,Larry,0,0,0,,We're heading away from the designated landing spot.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:17.01,0:17:21.57,Default,Larry,0,0,0,,At this rate, we'll have to land in a rocky area, thirty kilometers away.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:21.57,0:17:23.31,Default,Larry,0,0,0,,What do we do, Houston?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:23.31,0:17:25.44,Default,Larry,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}What do we do, Houston?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:23.31,0:17:25.44,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:25.44,0:17:26.65,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:26.93,0:17:29.54,Default,Dami,0,0,0,,We confirm the warning.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:29.54,0:17:32.65,Default,Dami,0,0,0,,We will search for a safe landing area, and communicate it to you.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:36.27,0:17:38.20,Default,A,0,0,0,,CAPCOM, what's going on?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:47.67,0:17:49.00,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Butler...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:49.74,0:17:51.92,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does NASA truly believe...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:52.78,0:17:57.38,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}that Hibito is an unfortunate and weak person?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:57.38,0:18:00.64,Default,But,0,0,0,,N-No, certainly not.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:01.55,0:18:04.06,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}In my mind, Hibito is the exact opposite.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:07.04,0:18:08.63,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}After the lunar accident,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:08.63,0:18:11.60,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}he saved his fellow crew member from the bottom of a dark ravine,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:11.60,0:18:14.39,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}making all the right decisions to return alive.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:15.52,0:18:20.78,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Afterward, he demonstrated that he had conquered his panic disorder.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:22.18,0:18:27.93,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hibito knows the fear of being in space better than any other astronaut,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:27.93,0:18:30.13,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}and he has overcome that fear!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:33.82,0:18:35.96,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you ask me,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:36.60,0:18:38.84,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}he is the ultimate astronaut.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:49.88,0:18:50.97,Default,But,0,0,0,,I feel
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.56,0:18:53.83,Default,But,0,0,0,,the same way.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:05.53,0:19:07.33,Default,But,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Butler.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:08.30,0:19:10.16,Default,Hoshi,0,0,0,,It's been a while since we last talked, Butler.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:11.16,0:19:15.10,Default,But,0,0,0,,It's unusual for you to give me a call,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:15.95,0:19:17.17,Default,But,0,0,0,,Mr. Hoshika.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:21.67,0:19:23.91,Default,Hoshi,0,0,0,,Are you available to meet right now?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:23.91,0:19:28.02,Default,Hoshi,0,0,0,,I'm in Houston for a meeting on asteroids.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.58,0:19:31.91,Default,Hoshi,0,0,0,,I'd like to talk to you about Nanba Hibito.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:34.06,0:19:34.06,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:45.83,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,520)}The starlight illuminates my future, it's wow... truth
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:52.17,ED,,0,0,0,,It's 3 AM, and I dream awake
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:55.88,ED,,0,0,0,,With no idea of my future
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:20:01.18,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,521)}only impatience consumes me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:10.23,ED,,0,0,0,,I have a thorn in my heart that won't allow me to lose to him
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:15.40,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,519)}I'm walking a path of thorns I made for myself
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:21.03,ED,,0,0,0,,But I won't forget the love I found
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:24.74,ED,,0,0,0,,And I won't forget the ones close to me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:30.58,ED,,0,0,0,,I realized you cannot live your life alone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:38.25,ED,,0,0,0,,The starlight illuminates my future, and we are all shooting stars
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:46.30,ED,,0,0,0,,My holy wishes turn all our sad lies into something better
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:49.97,ED,,0,0,0,,Our orbits have gotten separated,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:54.77,ED,,0,0,0,,but I'm fine if you are close
