Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:06.57,preview,Mu,0,0,0,,Hibito has yet to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:12.37,preview,Mu,0,0,0,,But he has made a decision about his future as an astronaut.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:14.94,preview,Mu,0,0,0,,Next time, on {\i0}Space Brothers{\i1}:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:16.96,preview,Mu,0,0,0,,"People Change, Promises Don't"
Dialogue: 5,0:21:19.00,0:21:19.00,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Mr. Hibbit}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:19.80,0:21:21.62,Default,Fred,0,0,0,,Mr. Hibbit!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:30.34,0:21:35.69,Default,Hibbit,0,0,0,,I was hoping for one last bite of a space carrot...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:37.38,0:21:39.27,Default,Hibbit,0,0,0,,Wh-What's this light?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:39.27,0:21:40.50,Default,Hibbit,0,0,0,,I can't see...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:42.16,0:21:43.99,Default,Hibbit,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:43.99,0:21:50.53,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Sorry, I was curious about Earth's technology, so I was fiddling around your base.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:50.53,0:21:52.26,Default,Light,0,0,0,,I meant no harm.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:52.94,0:21:55.25,Default,Light,0,0,0,,As an apology, I'll give you this.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:56.38,0:21:57.58,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Take a bite.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:58.50,0:22:00.12,Default,Light,0,0,0,,You'll feel better.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:01.91,0:22:04.55,Default,Hibbit,0,0,0,,I-It tastes great!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:05.66,0:22:08.83,Default,Hibbit,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:10.62,0:22:11.62,Default,Hibbit,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:17.73,0:22:20.08,Default,Buddy,0,0,0,,You okay, Hibbit?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:20.08,0:22:21.88,Default,Linda,0,0,0,,Hibbit!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:21.88,0:22:22.87,Default,Dami,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:22.87,0:22:23.90,Default,Fred,0,0,0,,Hibbit.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:23.90,0:22:25.36,Default,Karen,0,0,0,,Let me look at him.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:30.80,0:22:33.58,Default,Karen,0,0,0,,Strange... Nothing's wrong with him.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:35.74,0:22:37.83,Default,Hibbit,0,0,0,,The moon rabbit saved me.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:38.16,0:22:39.41,Default,Fred,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:39.41,0:22:41.96,Default,Karen,0,0,0,,Oh, it appears something {\i1}is{\i0} wrong with him.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:42.24,0:22:44.94,Default,Hibbit,0,0,0,,It was totally worth the trip up here!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:44.94,0:22:46.51,Default,Hibbit,0,0,0,,Let's fix up the base quick...
Dialogue: 5,0:22:47.88,0:22:50.47,Default,Hibbit,0,0,0,,And go find them!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:51.59,0:22:54.93,Default,Hibbit,0,0,0,,I'm sure they're somewhere on the moon.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:55.82,0:22:58.53,Default,Hibbit,0,0,0,,Wait for us, moon rabbits!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:58.53,0:23:00.60,Default,Hibbit,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:16.16,0:23:19.77,Default,Both,0,0,0,,And that's the end!
